data.text:
offensive slang

written abbreviation for what the fuck: a rude phrase used, for example in text messages and on social networking websites, to show that you are surprised or annoyed, or do not care about something

(Definition of wtf from the Cambridge Advanced Learner's Dictionary & Thesaurus © Cambridge University Press)
